data.description: Welcome home! This stunning two-story residence boasts four spacious bedrooms and two and a half luxurious bathrooms, offering ample space for comfortable living. The modern kitchen features newer appliances with an open concept perfect to entertain. With its prime location in close proximity to schools, parks, and amenities, this home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
